{"tid":944550,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"袁木死後，遇見了天使。天使：你可以上天堂","createTime":"2018-12-17T08:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T08:52:49.000Z","uid":19408,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"273b216cc402e6aa2b45cc5a822d61cd989409f1","tid":944550,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:31:24.000Z","msg":"天使對他說：「你可以上天堂。」袁木沒想到自己這麼仆街也能上天堂，心裏暗喜，便問：「為什麼？」<br />\n天使回答：徇眾要求。<br />\n袁木十分興奮，他就知道黨不會忘記他。<br />\n天使繼續說：「你不是說天安門沒死一個人嗎？那2000人想你也上天堂，好把你煎皮拆骨。」<br />\n袁木：「我還是下地獄算了，饒了我吧！」"},{"pid":"32c0a3e909eec797041d34a36248a26fd5af8777","tid":944550,"uid":19408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"天使：「求饒？大遲！」"},{"pid":"e9461a58a550c5c026cd6f87e02e45faa992deac","tid":944550,"uid":38030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"袁木求饒"},{"pid":"0c1841c87b5809a56fee876a87480e8aaccbe0db","tid":944550,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61713bee94f196b7025ad6e943d291fb860ca0c7","tid":944550,"uid":69090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:50:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5008bef750c79705bc5df4293dacf830183daeb","tid":944550,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9461a58a550c5c026cd6f87e02e45faa992deac","tid":944550,"uid":38030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:33:27.000Z","msg":"袁木求饒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc29fa494f53c23148914d47e84e967163c48798","tid":9